Specifically, ultrapowers embeds text from Superpowers (version 5.1.0), the TDD
and SDD skill content verbatim, and the two reviewer briefs sourced/adapted from it,
used to give the build harness behavioral parity with the Superpowers skills it
descends from:

  - workflow/ultrapowers-development.js : the embedded `TDD_SKILL` string is the
    verbatim content of superpowers:test-driven-development/SKILL.md
  - workflow/ultrapowers-development.js : the embedded `SDD_GUIDANCE` string is
    sourced verbatim from superpowers:subagent-driven-development/implementer-prompt.md
  - workflow/ultrapowers-development.js : the spec-compliance reviewer prompt is
    sourced from superpowers:subagent-driven-development/spec-reviewer-prompt.md
  - workflow/ultrapowers-development.js : the code-quality reviewer prompt is
    sourced from superpowers:subagent-driven-development/code-quality-reviewer-prompt.md

